subject: Swine Influenza
Colleges and Universities
Influenza
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Tulane, Duke, Alabama and Texas Christian have reported players who have swine flu or flulike symptoms. Health experts say college athletes are perfect candidates to become ill.
